</div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>I got endings from A to D, how to get other 2?<br>I found password, but what is it for? TvT<br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-7994504" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7994504,&quot;user_id&quot;:4762296}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/axelvejardossow"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzExOTI5MDcwLnBuZw==/25x25%23/k50CAJ.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axelvejardossow">Axel Vejar Dossow</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-06-21 13:37:29"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7994504">8 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>******SPOILERS*******</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Ending E: get the shotgun, kill the twins, kill the mother, kill Greta. Go to the second floor, to the stairs near the family pictures. It should take you to Mr. Bob&#x27;s room</p><p><br></p><p>Ending F: get the shotgun, kill the family, but also have the ball and the holy candle in your inventory, and watch the videotape in the studio room (one of the rooms in the hallway where you were captured by the mother). Then go to Mr. Bob&#x27;s room<br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>********************************************</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-7994799" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7994799,&quot;user_id&quot;:5036780}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/abra-geroni"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEwMTMyNjMxLmpwZw==/25x25%23/R1S7uR.jpg)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/abra-geroni">Abra Geroni</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-06-21 14:43:14"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7994799">8 days ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(3 edits)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Ok<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>Now I got all endings, but still don&#x27;t understand - who&#x27;s mister Bob? What&#x27;s his connection with Alesa? And a lot more:&gt;<br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-7994881" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7994881,&quot;user_id&quot;:4762296}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/axelvejardossow"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzExOTI5MDcwLnBuZw==/25x25%23/k50CAJ.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axelvejardossow">Axel Vejar Dossow</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-06-21 14:54:33"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7994881">8 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>When you watch the video tape, little Alesa says: &quot;I want a new family, I want a new house&quot;. Mr. Bob was the one who recorded that video and wanted to grant Alesa her wish: a new house/family for Alesa.&nbsp;</p><p>I would say he&#x27;s a demonic entity with limited reality warping powers who is obssesed with Alesa. His ultimate goal seems to be to turn Alesa into an amorphous blob and be with her forever...or at least until he gets bored of her and looks for another victim.</p><p>The inside of the house is actually in a different plane, that&#x27;s why the police can&#x27;t find anything. <br></p><p>I&#x27;m not sure myself though. And Mr. Bob might return in some of my next projects, who knows...</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-7994980" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7994980,&quot;user_id&quot;:5036780}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxelvejardossow.itch.io%2Fa-house-for-alesa&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_